data.description: Well Priced 4-Plex (TownHome Style), Two 2Bdrm-1.5Bath, Two 3Bdrm-1.5Bath, Plenty of room to increase rents.  Recent shingles (2019yr), Each unit has it's own full size W/D connections inside and private back patio space, Seperatly metered for electricity & water.  Conveniently located near downtown Florence and shopping, Only 19 miles to Georgetown AND 28 miles to Round Rock...  4.625% FHA Mortgage is qualify assumable (approx $320k balance), Low Property Tax Rate (2.377), All tenants are on a month/month lease.  Sorry, no showings until under contract.
